title: Dyson V6 Absolute Cordless Vacuum 209560-01 - Overview
description:
Dyson V6 Absolute Cordless Vacuum - 209560-01 http://www.abt.com/product/89083/Dyson-20956001.html

The Dyson V6 Absolute cordless vacuum comes equipped with two Dyson-engineered cleaner heads. Invented for hard floors the Soft roller cleaner head removes large debris and fine dust simultaneously. The Direct-drive cleaner head provides 75 more power than the Dyson V6 vacuum. HEPA filtration captures allergens and expels cleaner air. Extra Dyson-engineered tools for homes with pets.
Features:
• Soft roller cleaner head removes large debris and fine dust simultaneously
• Direct-drive cleaner head with 75 more brush bar power than the Dyson V6 vacuum
• HEPA Filtration to capture allergens and expel cleaner air.
• Removes 99.97 of particles as small as 0.3 microns.
• The Dyson digital motor V6 creates the most powerful cordless vacuum
• 2 Tier RadialTM cyclones capture more fine dust
• Balanced for cleaning up top down below and in between
• Up to 20 minutes of powerful fade-free suction
• Mini motorized tool removes pet hair and ground-in dirt
• Mini soft dusting brush gently removes dust from around the home
• Max mode gives stronger suction for more difficult tasks
• Docking station stores and charges the machine so its ready to use
• Hygienic bin emptying – just push the button to release the dirt
• Wand detaches easily for handheld cleaning
• Click-fit cleaning tools for all round cleaning
• Built from the strongest materials available to ensure
